{"content_hash": "sha256:b4a0da2b80982d0409740f07c6ef005a8d9dee134a29d5250b9a52def59fdf12", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0121", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "Over the last few months, our team @GoogleDeepMind  and @googlecloud has been putting  our Gemini-powered algorithm discovery agent AlphaEvolve to work across a wide variety of important applications. The results are amazing!\n\nWe're seeing ", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "D-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "Over the last few months, our team @GoogleDeepMind  and @googlecloud has been putting  our Gemini-powered algorithm disc", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/pushmeet/status/2052507929153294387", "summary_for_indexing": "Over the last few months, our team @GoogleDeepMind  and @googlecloud has been putting  our Gemini-powered algorithm discovery agent AlphaEvolve to work across a wide variety of important applications. The results are amazing!\n\nWe're seeing major improvements in everything from chip design and genomics to logistics, electric grid optimization, and earth sciences. And this impact will only grow once it's used on more problems! 🚀 A perfect example of how AI agents will shape the world. \n\nRead more "}
{"content_hash": "sha256:7de8954fe0101c6bbe217953238d102717dc14419397d376f477eb47397b3235", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0122", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT Artificial Analysis\nOpenAI has released GPT-Realtime-2, achieving 96.6% in our Speech Reasoning benchmark, Big Bench Audio, and #1 in our Conversational Dynamics benchmark\n\nReleased today, GPT-Realtime-2 is OpenAI's new flagship native S", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT Artificial Analysis", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052521826774057015", "summary_for_indexing": "RT Artificial Analysis\nOpenAI has released GPT-Realtime-2, achieving 96.6% in our Speech Reasoning benchmark, Big Bench Audio, and #1 in our Conversational Dynamics benchmark\n\nReleased today, GPT-Realtime-2 is OpenAI's new flagship native Speech to Speech model, introducing adjustable reasoning effort levels from minimal through to xHigh. The high variant achieves a Big Bench Audio result of 96.6% equal to Gemini 3.1 Flash Live Preview - High. GPT-Realtime-2 continues to lead our Conversational "}
{"content_hash": "sha256:bbe32ec250a4624499b26b080cb2acd560a0510047134ea84192bcc213b57513", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0123", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT dominik kundel\nOne of the coolest things with Codex for Chrome is combining it with subagents so you can test things like multiplayer games! \n\nAvailable for both macOS and Windows.\n\nHappy Codexing", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT dominik kundel", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052487869655343427", "summary_for_indexing": "RT dominik kundel\nOne of the coolest things with Codex for Chrome is combining it with subagents so you can test things like multiplayer games! \n\nAvailable for both macOS and Windows.\n\nHappy Codexing"}
