{"content_hash": "sha256:8ad4474535bd0eda391eab6f109410706b809317acb2063b0c3eb306e0469d4e", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0125", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT Andrew Ambrosino\nnew: Codex can now drive tabs in Chrome, working in background tabs alongside you. Get the new Chrome extension today.\n\nalso: we shipped a ton of performance improvements in the app. should feel a lot better.\n\nhappy code", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT Andrew Ambrosino", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052493576026911228", "summary_for_indexing": "RT Andrew Ambrosino\nnew: Codex can now drive tabs in Chrome, working in background tabs alongside you. Get the new Chrome extension today.\n\nalso: we shipped a ton of performance improvements in the app. should feel a lot better.\n\nhappy codexing!"}
{"content_hash": "sha256:38c3d59bed4f8d5597f3fb411118f4a7fd5d24fd6908609ba3277ea4316329e4", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0126", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT Scale Labs\nCongrats to @OpenAI for taking the top spot on our Audio MultiChallenge S2S leaderboard with the release of GPT‑Realtime‑2 🥇\n\nGPT-Realtime-2 more than doubles GPT-Realtime-1.5 on instruction retention, rising from 36.7% to 70.", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT Scale Labs", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052454371729031300", "summary_for_indexing": "RT Scale Labs\nCongrats to @OpenAI for taking the top spot on our Audio MultiChallenge S2S leaderboard with the release of GPT‑Realtime‑2 🥇\n\nGPT-Realtime-2 more than doubles GPT-Realtime-1.5 on instruction retention, rising from 36.7% to 70.8% APR, and also stands out on voice editing, especially when users repair or revise what they are saying in real time – crucial for voice agent use cases.\n\nExcited to see the pace of progress as voice AI accelerates."}
{"content_hash": "sha256:cf8b6906416e22a93c2366226c3e9d6fff261a4d767079210624338a28c4b51b", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0127", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT Vimeo\nDubbing for live events… in real time? 😮\n\nHere’s OpenAI’s new GPT-Realtime-Translate model in action in Vimeo.\n\nThose translations are happening completely live. No pre-loaded captions.\n\nLive dubbing is one of the many features we’", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT Vimeo", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052446813597380936", "summary_for_indexing": "RT Vimeo\nDubbing for live events… in real time? 😮\n\nHere’s OpenAI’s new GPT-Realtime-Translate model in action in Vimeo.\n\nThose translations are happening completely live. No pre-loaded captions.\n\nLive dubbing is one of the many features we’re exploring this year...\n\n(Hopefully) more soon.\n\nBut in the meantime, we just had to show you!\n\nBravo @OpenAIDevs  👏"}
{"content_hash": "sha256:aecfcf93ee3e036f48c30143fd66f2ae31ec07a71f660e886ee2fe08bd5f5ffc", "degraded": false, "evidence_id": "EVD-20260508-0128", "kiq_hint": [], "language": "en", "quotable_excerpt": "RT Glean\nTaking talking shop to a whole new level.\n\nWe just shipped Glean’s real-time voice capability, powered by @OpenAI’s newest speech model GPT-Realtime-2.\n\nGrounded in the context across your org, it feels like a real AI coworker and ", "raw_path": "Information/raw/2026-05-08/x_posts.jsonl", "reliability_admiralty": "A-3", "retrieval_method": "rsshub", "retrieved_at": "2026-05-08T08:04:25+09:00", "run_date": "2026-05-08", "schema_version": "1.0", "source_title": "RT Glean", "source_type": "social", "source_url": "https://x.com/OpenAIDevs/status/2052442307031609541", "summary_for_indexing": "RT Glean\nTaking talking shop to a whole new level.\n\nWe just shipped Glean’s real-time voice capability, powered by @OpenAI’s newest speech model GPT-Realtime-2.\n\nGrounded in the context across your org, it feels like a real AI coworker and can keep up with how work gets finished.\n\nIn internal evals, GPT-Realtime-2 delivered a 42.9% relative increase in helpfulness over its previous version.\n\nGive it a try. It speaks for itself.\n\n@OpenAIDevs"}
